---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="I'm New">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 space-y-8">
    <h1 class="heading-eden-gold theme-display-font text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold">I'm New</h1>

    <section class="bg-white border-2 border-[var(--ink)] p-8 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--ink)]">When does church happen?</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink)]/90">We gather to worship every Sunday morning at 10:45am. We also run activities during the week for children, local community support, and smaller groups.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white border-2 border-[var(--ink)] p-8 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--ink)]">What happens in a church service?</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink)]/90">The service is usually a little over an hour. We sing together, read the Bible, hear teaching that connects Scripture to everyday life, and spend time in prayer.</p>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink)]/90">On the first Sunday of each month, we also share Communion together.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white border-2 border-[var(--ink)] p-8 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--ink)]">What about children and young people?</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink)]/90">Children are very welcome. Most Sundays there is a children’s activity or children’s club during the service, and we work to help families feel at home.</p>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink)]/90">For more details, visit <a href="/park-kids" class="underline decoration-[var(--eden)] underline-offset-4">Park Kids</a> and <a href="/park-youth" class="underline decoration-[var(--teal)] underline-offset-4">Park Youth</a>.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
